meta {
  name: Activate a device
  type: http
  seq: 4
}

post {
  url: {{orgUrl}}/api/v1/devices/{{deviceId}}/lifecycle/activate
  body: none
  auth: none
}

headers {
  Accept: application/json
  Authorization: SSWS {{apiKey}}
}

docs {
Activates a device by setting its status to `ACTIVE` by `deviceId`.
Activated devices are used to create and delete device user links.

**Responses:**
- `204`: No Content
- `403`: 
- `404`: 
- `429`:
}
